packets.name: PIXLwear P1 Sneaker (Wolf Grey), right
packets.author: Pixls
packets.description:
PRODUCT WARNING: Wearing this sneaker during a full moon can have unintended side effects!

The PIXLwear P1 sneaker is a Cryptovoxels shoe for every situation. Comfortable, yet stylish. High-quality, yet affordable. The P1 model rocks the iconic PIXLwear colours for the tie-free laces and the PIXL P1 stamp on the sole. The insoles are stamped with “P” and “1” on the left and right shoe, respectively. This is the right shoe in the colour palette “Wolf Grey”. Designer: Pixls.eth. Manufactured with MagicaVoxel. PIXLwear: a PIXL brand - ethical blockchain fashion from Austria.
